			Company Description 
		


                Helix TCS, Inc. engages in the provision of software solutions and other related services in the cannabis industry. Its services include compliance software, assessment services, banking, security systems, and others. The company was founded in 2003 and is headquartered in Greenwood Village, CO.
            




